    "description": "隨著世界潮流對身心障礙者權益的重視，以及保障與落實人權平等觀念的日益提升，建構一個無障礙生活環境，使身心障礙者於醫療、學業及就業等各方面，能在機會均等及公平權益下參與社會各項活動，是未來重要的課題。",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "各單元主題如下：<br>1.身心障礙者的定義<br>2.身心障礙者的照顧<br>3.無障礙環境法規<br>4.無障礙環境定義<br>5.身心障礙者相關社會資源<br>6.身心障礙體驗之旅<br>7.無障礙環境與相關設施設計<br>8.無障礙環境控制<br>9.同學分組上臺簡報。指導與說明。學生演講錄影影片 PO上「Flip 數位學習」，班上師生彼此觀摩學習。<br>10.無障礙環境設施使用<br>11.身心障礙者之自立生活<br>12.身心障礙者職場的職務再設計<br>13.科技輔具在無障礙環境的應用<br>14.友善無障礙環境發展現況<br>15.創造未來無障礙環境<br>16.規劃無障礙的硬體與軟體環境<br>",
        "en": "Topics and Units are as Fellows:<br>1.\tDefinition of the handicap<br>2.\tCare for the handicap<br>3.\tLaws and regulations of accessible environment<br>4.\tDefinition of accessible environment<br>5.\tSocial resources for the handicap<br>6.\tHandicap experience journey <br>7.\tDesigning and developing accessible environment<br>8.\tEnvironment control of accessible environment<br>9.\tGroup presentation and discussion <br>10.\tAccessibility of handicap facilities<br>11.\tIndependent living for the handicap<br>12.\tJob accommodation and redesign for the handicap<br>13.\tAssistive technology device of accessible environment<br>14.\tFriendly accessible environment<br>15.\tFuture of accessible environment<br>16.\tPlanning of applying software and hardware design on friendly accessible environment<br><br>"
    },
